Subject: [PATCH 9/9] MAINTAINERS: add Allwinner sun60i pattern

Add the sun60i naming pattern to the Allwinner sunXi entry so A733
files are matched by both directory coverage and SoC-family naming.

Signed-off-by: Enzo Adriano <enzo.adriano.code@gmail.com>
---
 MAINTAINERS | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/MAINTAINERS b/MAINTAINERS
index 9ec290e38b44..7452b92768bd 100644
--- a/MAINTAINERS
+++ b/MAINTAINERS
@@ -2416,6 +2416,7 @@ F:	drivers/clk/sunxi-ng/
 F:	drivers/pinctrl/sunxi/
 F:	drivers/soc/sunxi/
 N:	allwinner
+N:	sun60i
 N:	sun[x456789]i
 N:	sun[25]0i
 
